title: Canopy HortPark All-Day Dining Restaurant
blurb: All-day dining surrounded by lush greenery.
description: Canopy HortPark features an all-day dining restaurant surrounded by lush greenery. Be tantalised by an extensive menu including brunch items, pastas, burgers, pizzas, mains and more. Bring your furry friends along too! Enjoy a relaxing meal in a beautiful garden setting. The restaurant offers a diverse menu to cater to different tastes, making it a perfect spot for families and friends. With its pet-friendly environment, you can bring your beloved furry companions along for a delightful dining experience. The restaurant provides a welcoming atmosphere for all.
Keyword_tag: cafe, Brunch, Pastas, Burgers, Pizzas, Pet-friendly, Garden

title: Restaurant Espoir: Modern European Cuisine
blurb: Refined Modern European Cuisine laced with Malayan.
description: Located in the historical Anglo-Chinese School in the CBD, Restaurant Espoir offers Halal Modern European Cuisine with Malayan influences. Ideal for corporate lunches, romantic dinners, teatime with friends, or family brunches. Expect creative menus, impeccable service, and a charming ambience. The restaurant aims to exceed expectations with its unique culinary offerings and welcoming atmosphere, making it a great choice for various occasions. The menu features a blend of classic European dishes with a local twist, ensuring a memorable dining experience for all guests.
price_display: Varies according to menu item. Kids dine free on weekends.

title: IKEA Swedish Restaurant
blurb: Check out our special menu and our all-time favourites!
description: The IKEA Swedish Restaurant offers a variety of dishes, including Swedish meatballs, salmon, and vegetarian options. It's a family-friendly dining option within the IKEA store, providing a convenient place to eat while shopping. The restaurant aims to provide affordable and tasty meals for all customers. Enjoy a range of Swedish cuisine in a casual setting, perfect for a quick bite or a relaxed meal with family and friends. The restaurant is designed to cater to families with children, offering a comfortable and welcoming atmosphere.

title: IKEA Restaurant Tampines
blurb: Enjoy special menus and all-time favourite dishes!
description: IKEA Restaurant Tampines offers a variety of dining options, including hot dishes, cold dishes, soups, and desserts. Check out our special menu and all-time favourites! Highlights include World Vegetarian Day & World Food Day, Deepavali, Monthly IKEA Family meal offer, Breakfast Menu, Hot dishes, Cold dishes, Soups, Desserts, Add On, Cold beverages, and Hot beverages. Restaurant opening hours: 10am-9.30pm with last order at 9pm (Mon-Fri) & 9am-10pm with last order at 9.30pm (Sat-Sun).

title: Restaurant Espoir: Le Petit Chef Dining Experience
blurb: An immersive culinary journey with Le Petit Chef!
description: Restaurant Espoir (Singapore) offers a unique theatre and dining experience with Le Petit Chef, the world's smallest chef. From June 2024, weekend lunch shows are tailored to be kid-friendly, welcoming children of all ages. Evening shows have a minimum age requirement of 5 years. The show features shared seating, with tables accommodating up to 4 guests.
price_display: Junior menu $98++, Petit chef and vegan menu $188++, Supreme chef menu $238++, Kids dine free for Weekend lunch during September

title: Splash Tribe at The Palawan @ Sentosa
blurb: A fuss-free day out with distinct lounging areas.
description: Splash Tribe offers a daycation destination with various amenities and refreshments. It features pools suitable for all ages, including kids-friendly pools and an infinity-edge pool by the beach. Guests can also relax in exclusive two-storey gazebos with views of the pools and beach, adding a touch of exclusivity to their visit. Enjoy a splashing good time with family and friends at this vibrant destination. The venue provides a range of options for relaxation and recreation, ensuring a memorable experience for all visitors. With its thoughtful amenities and diverse pool options, Splash Tribe is an ideal spot for a family day out.
full_address: 54 Palawan Beach Walk, The Palawan @ Sentosa, 098233
